articles.title: Somebody once told me the world is gonna roll me
articles.content:
I ain’t the sharpest tool in the shed
She was looking kind of dumb with her finger and her thumb
In the shape of an “L” on her forehead

authors.name: Benedict Cucumberbatch
authors.biography: Benedict was a renowned investigator before becoming a doctor with magical and powerful powers. But he was so bored by Disney's greed  so that is why he became a journalist for some fictional blog.

authors.name: Martin Unfreeman
authors.biography: After helping Benedict Cucumberbatch during his investigations in England, he had decided to live as a survivalist in a small and hidden house, until some greyish magician knocked on his door. As being always nearly close to death was annoying him, he reconverted himself as a ghost writer for his best friend forever.
